1
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,660
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">There we go...</font>

2
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:59,190
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Make sure you listen to your uncle.</font>

3
00:00:59,190 --> 00:01:00,360
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

4
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:02,240
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Do you have your handkerchief? Your ticket?</font>

5
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:04,360
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">A nice pair of shoes?</font>

6
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,780
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Wait, don't tell me that's everything?</font>

7
00:01:05,780 --> 00:01:08,040
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's fine. I made sure I packed the black ones.</font>

8
00:01:08,950 --> 00:01:11,670
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Make sure you don't forget your luggage on the bullet train, okay?</font>

9
00:01:11,670 --> 00:01:13,800
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Don't zone out and miss your stop.</font>

10
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,300
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah, I got it!</font>

11
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:19,150
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Jeez. I've been going there every year, so I'll be all right.</font>

12
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:22,630
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hey, put on a hat. You'll get heat stroke.</font>

13
00:01:22,630 --> 00:01:25,060
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's alright! I'm fine.</font>

14
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,900
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">See you!</font>

15
00:01:57,130 --> 00:01:59,220
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>The first time I met him</i></font>

16
00:02:01,470 --> 00:02:03,560
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>was when I was six.</i></font>

17
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:12,900
<font face="Constantia" size="110" color="#e4f0fb">{\an8}To the Forest of Firefly Lights</font>

18
00:02:14,010 --> 00:02:15,950
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>On a hot summer day,</i></font>

19
00:02:15,950 --> 00:02:19,260
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I got lost in the forest of the mountain god,</i></font>

20
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:21,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>which was said to be where spirits lived.</i></font>

21
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:27,550
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>After running around searching for an exit</i></font>

22
00:02:27,550 --> 00:02:29,620
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I became so tired I couldn't move.</i></font>

23
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:35,140
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>When I started crying from fear and loneliness,</i></font>

24
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:38,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>he appeared before me.</i></font>

25
00:02:41,250 --> 00:02:42,800
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hey! Shorty!</font>

26
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:04,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Why are you crying?</font>

27
00:03:08,270 --> 00:03:11,660
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's a person! I'm saved!</font>

28
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,180
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">S-Sorry.</font>

29
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:31,390
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're a human child, right?</font>

30
00:03:32,580 --> 00:03:35,860
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If a human touches me, I'll disappear.</font>

31
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:40,390
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If a human...?</font>

32
00:03:41,070 --> 00:03:43,210
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're not a human?</font>

33
00:03:44,410 --> 00:03:47,170
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm... something that lives in this forest.</font>

34
00:03:48,890 --> 00:03:51,590
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">What? Then... you're one of the spirits?</font>

35
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:56,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But... what do you mean by disappear?</font>

36
00:04:21,130 --> 00:04:24,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Y-You're really not human after all...</font>

37
00:04:27,070 --> 00:04:31,570
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No human would hit a child like that!</font>

38
00:04:32,970 --> 00:04:37,130
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">To disappear means to be obliterated.</font>

39
00:04:38,780 --> 00:04:42,790
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's the spell that the mountain god placed upon me.</font>

40
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:46,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If I get touched by a human,</font>

41
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,260
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">that's the end.</font>

42
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:55,050
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I-I'm sorry.</font>

43
00:04:55,050 --> 00:04:56,660
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Here, shorty.</font>

44
00:04:57,730 --> 00:04:59,190
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Grab the other end.</font>

45
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:01,340
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're lost, aren't you?</font>

46
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,460
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'll lead you out of the forest.</font>

47
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:08,320
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank you!</font>

48
00:05:12,970 --> 00:05:14,030
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Didn't I just tell you?</font>

49
00:05:14,030 --> 00:05:17,080
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Sorry, I just...</font>

50
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,450
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's just like going on a date!</font>

51
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:36,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Not a very romantic one...</font>

52
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:46,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You... aren't afraid.</font>

53
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:49,620
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Of what?</font>

54
00:05:50,910 --> 00:05:51,670
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Never mind.</font>

55
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:58,400
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If you go straight, you'll hit the mountain path.</font>

56
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:00,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Bye.</font>

57
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:04,240
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Are you always going to be here?</font>

58
00:06:05,090 --> 00:06:07,090
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If I come back here, can we meet again?</font>

59
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:10,870
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This is the forest where the mountain god and spirits live.</font>

60
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:14,970
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Set foot within, and you'll lose your way and be lost forever.</font>

61
00:06:16,690 --> 00:06:17,940
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You shouldn't come here.</font>

62
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:21,110
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's what the villagers say, right?</font>

63
00:06:25,650 --> 00:06:27,900
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm Takegawa Hotaru.</font>

64
00:06:28,410 --> 00:06:29,110
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You?</font>

65
00:06:49,030 --> 00:06:52,700
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Anyway, I'll be back tomorrow with a thank-you present!</font>

66
00:06:52,700 --> 00:06:53,510
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Bye!</font>

67
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,640
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's Gin.</font>

68
00:07:13,730 --> 00:07:14,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru!</font>

69
00:07:14,530 --> 00:07:16,320
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, Uncle!</font>

70
00:07:17,590 --> 00:07:21,010
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru, you idiot!</font>

71
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:24,850
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If you go into the forest on your own and get hurt, what are you gonna do?</font>

72
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,640
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Uncle.</font>

73
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,620
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Huh?</font>

74
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:43,100
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is it true that there are spirits living in that forest?</font>

75
00:07:43,710 --> 00:07:46,950
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh, the mountain god's forest... Who knows.</font>

76
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,780
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's what they say.</font>

77
00:07:53,940 --> 00:07:58,840
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">When I was little, I wanted to meet the spirits, so my friends and I often went into the forest.</font>

78
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:05,350
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">In the end, I never met any, but I had the feeling I'd occasionally spot something from the corner of my eye.</font>

79
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:11,410
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">On summer nights, you could hear the sounds of the river coming from the forest.{*TLC hayashi?}</font>

80
00:08:11,410 --> 00:08:18,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">And now that I think about it, Iwa said she and her friends went and had fun at a summer festival in the forest.</font>

81
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:22,830
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But there's no way the villagers would've held a festival in the forest.</font>

82
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:25,950
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">So then, whose festival could it have been?</font>

83
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:32,490
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It started this crazy story that they must've snuck into a festival for the spirits.</font>

84
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:38,220
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Man, that takes me back!</font>

85
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:41,500
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">We were so stupid back when we were kids.</font>

86
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:15,060
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is the forest where the mountain god and spirits live.</i></font>

87
00:09:16,430 --> 00:09:18,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Set foot within, and you'll lose your way and be lost forever.</i></font>

88
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,560
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You came.</font>

89
00:09:46,110 --> 00:09:48,380
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I didn't think you'd really come back.</font>

90
00:09:49,490 --> 00:09:50,250
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You...</font>

91
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:54,570
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You waited for me!</font>

92
00:09:59,330 --> 00:10:01,470
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You just don't learn, do you?</font>

93
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:04,210
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I was so happy, I just...</font>

94
00:10:04,210 --> 00:10:05,390
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Sorry.</font>

95
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,790
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's a bit hot here.</font>

96
00:10:09,630 --> 00:10:11,090
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Shall we go somewhere cooler?</font>

97
00:10:11,450 --> 00:10:12,080
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">What?</font>

98
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:14,180
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Don't worry.</font>

99
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,090
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'll see you out of here again.</font>

100
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:12,470
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin.</font>

101
00:11:13,370 --> 00:11:16,730
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is that a human child?</font>

102
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:20,240
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Can I eat it?</font>

103
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:22,950
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No.</font>

104
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:24,740
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">She's my friend.</font>

105
00:11:25,230 --> 00:11:26,600
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is that so?</font>

106
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,630
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Human child.</font>

107
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:32,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Please don't touch Gin's skin.</font>

108
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:38,260
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If you do, I'll eat you!</font>

109
00:11:43,650 --> 00:11:45,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh! Is that a fox?</font>

110
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:50,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">He's another one of the spirits.</font>

111
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:55,450
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">He transforms to scare people, but he's all bark and no bite.{He transforms to scare people, but he's actually cowardly and a good guy.}</font>

112
00:11:59,210 --> 00:12:01,000
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Amazing!</font>

113
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:04,030
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This is the first time I've seen a real spirit!</font>

114
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:05,460
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">So they really do exist!</font>

115
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:09,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Amazing! Incredible! Fantastic!</font>

116
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:09,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">{\an8}So what did you think I was?</font>

117
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:15,540
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin, are you a No-Face or something?</font>

118
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:18,280
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Why do you wear a mask?</font>

119
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,750
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No particular reason.</font>

120
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:22,850
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Never mind me.</font>

121
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:24,800
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Tell me about yourself.</font>

122
00:12:26,830 --> 00:12:27,800
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Are you curious?</font>

123
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,810
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's why I waited for you.</font>

124
00:12:38,690 --> 00:12:43,700
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>The next day and the day after that, I went back to the forest.</i></font>

125
00:12:45,530 --> 00:12:50,070
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Those summer days, I ran and played all around the mountain.</i></font>

126
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:55,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Over here, over here!</font>

127
00:12:56,650 --> 00:12:58,490
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's better over there.</font>

128
00:13:01,420 --> 00:13:02,340
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">There.</font>

129
00:13:03,490 --> 00:13:04,330
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank you!</font>

130
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:15,380
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Even though it was silly,</i></font>

131
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:18,110
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>it was so much fun.</i></font>

132
00:13:42,110 --> 00:13:45,130
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Did Gin fall asleep?</font>

133
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:56,310
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>It's fine if I touch his mask, right?</i></font>

134
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:15,600
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, sorry!</font>

135
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,000
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ouch!</font>

136
00:14:18,010 --> 00:14:22,120
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Attacking someone while they're asleep... You sure are a scary little lady.</font>

137
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,500
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm sorry, but</font>

138
00:14:25,190 --> 00:14:27,300
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">you were pretending to sleep, weren't you?</font>

139
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:31,090
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I looked normal, didn't I?</font>

140
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:35,570
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Why are you wearing that mask?</font>

141
00:14:36,570 --> 00:14:38,390
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If I don't wear this mask,</font>

142
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,790
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I don't look like a spirit, do I?</font>

143
00:14:52,630 --> 00:14:53,880
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're weird.</font>

144
00:15:02,290 --> 00:15:03,670
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Um, Gin.</font>

145
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:07,280
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I won't be able</font>

146
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:09,960
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">to come here tomorrow.</font>

147
00:15:11,060 --> 00:15:12,880
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I told you about it before, right?</font>

148
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:16,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That I'm just staying at my uncle's place for the summer?</font>

149
00:15:17,170 --> 00:15:20,760
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">So I have to go home tomorrow.</font>

150
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Will you be able to come again next year?</font>

151
00:15:32,610 --> 00:15:33,450
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah!</font>

152
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:38,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is how summer</i></font>

153
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:42,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>became something I looked forward to.</i></font>

154
00:15:52,980 --> 00:15:57,470
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Gin waited for our promised summer.</i></font>

155
00:15:59,050 --> 00:16:00,820
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's cold!</font>

156
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:04,240
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're weird.</font>

157
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:06,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Of course the water is cold.</font>

158
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:19,790
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin!</font>

159
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,120
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin!</font>

160
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:24,810
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's dangerous, Gin.</font>

161
00:16:24,810 --> 00:16:27,090
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's a human child.</font>

162
00:16:27,090 --> 00:16:30,960
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If she touches you, you'll disappear.</font>

163
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,960
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank you.</font>

164
00:16:33,130 --> 00:16:34,220
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm fine.</font>

165
00:16:41,450 --> 00:16:45,110
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Please don't touch him, human child.</font>

166
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:47,370
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yes.</font>

167
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:57,730
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin.</font>

168
00:16:59,070 --> 00:17:00,160
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Be careful.</font>

169
00:17:04,090 --> 00:17:08,430
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">The spirits can touch him, right?</font>

170
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:13,670
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Two summers passed. Then three. {the original line for this is really bad, plz2tlc}</i></font>

171
00:17:15,150 --> 00:17:16,120
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru!</font>

172
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:19,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Where are you?</font>

173
00:17:22,340 --> 00:17:23,220
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru.</font>

174
00:17:24,050 --> 00:17:24,560
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hota—</font>

175
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,650
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">What're you doing?</font>

176
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:36,700
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I wanted to see your startled face, but...</font>

177
00:17:42,700 --> 00:17:44,220
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">At least when I'm around,</font>

178
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:47,360
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">can you take off your mask every once in a while?</font>

179
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:49,210
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's fine,</font>

180
00:17:49,870 --> 00:17:51,460
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">but is there a reason?</font>

181
00:17:52,050 --> 00:17:54,560
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Not really, but—</font>

182
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:57,470
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Watch out, Hota—</font>

183
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:11,310
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That was close.</font>

184
00:18:14,020 --> 00:18:15,490
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah...</font>

185
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:18,970
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm sorry, Hotaru.</font>

186
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:20,800
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Are you okay?</font>

187
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:26,780
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank goodness.</font>

188
00:18:28,730 --> 00:18:29,770
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hey, Gin.</font>

189
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:39,510
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No matter what, don't ever touch me, okay?</font>

190
00:18:44,930 --> 00:18:45,600
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Okay?</font>

191
00:18:55,910 --> 00:18:57,170
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No matter what!</font>

192
00:19:05,390 --> 00:19:09,000
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>The next summer and the summer after that</i></font>

193
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:12,280
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I visited the forest.</i></font>

194
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,600
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm leaving!</font>

195
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:28,510
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin! I'm here again this year.</font>

196
00:19:29,910 --> 00:19:30,890
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ta-da!</font>

197
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:33,540
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I've become a fifth grader.</font>

198
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:37,250
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Somehow,</font>

199
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,820
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">you're starting to look like a woman.</font>

200
00:19:40,140 --> 00:19:42,320
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I <i>am</i> a woman.</font>

201
00:19:43,490 --> 00:19:44,360
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Shall we go?</font>

202
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:47,350
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

203
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:48,040
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Huh?</i></font>

204
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:49,580
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is...</i></font>

205
00:19:56,340 --> 00:19:57,430
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh.</font>

206
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:58,830
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Huh?</font>

207
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:00,260
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Nothing.</font>

208
00:20:01,050 --> 00:20:02,700
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Even though I'm in middle school now,</font>

209
00:20:02,700 --> 00:20:07,820
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">a lot of my elementary school friends are in the same classes, so it doesn't really feel like anything changed.</font>

210
00:20:07,820 --> 00:20:11,580
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">{\an8}<i>Our ages are gradually getting closer.</i></font>

211
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:10,430
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But rather than that...</font>

212
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:18,660
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Somehow,</i></font>

213
00:20:19,290 --> 00:20:23,610
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Gin ages much more slowly than humans.</i></font>

214
00:20:30,430 --> 00:20:31,170
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Like this?</font>

215
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:35,460
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah, yeah. When I start running, let go, okay?</font>

216
00:20:37,860 --> 00:20:39,390
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Here I go!</font>

217
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:19,010
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>As the years go by, my appearance changes,</i></font>

218
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:24,260
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>but Gin is almost the same as the day we met.</i></font>

219
00:22:02,330 --> 00:22:06,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Someday I'll be older than Gin, won't I?</i></font>

220
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh, Hotaru.</font>

221
00:22:38,420 --> 00:22:40,330
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I cut some watermelon. Let's eat.</font>

222
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:42,890
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Okay. Yay!</font>

223
00:22:48,590 --> 00:22:49,600
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Where's Mom?</font>

224
00:22:50,170 --> 00:22:51,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Out shopping with your aunt.</font>

225
00:22:51,890 --> 00:22:54,460
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">They went to buy gifts for friends in Yokohama.</font>

226
00:22:56,760 --> 00:22:59,410
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">What time are you taking the bullet train tomorrow?</font>

227
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:01,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I don't know,</font>

228
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:04,260
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">but they said I'll still be here until the afternoon.</font>

229
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:06,340
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is that so?</font>

230
00:23:09,180 --> 00:23:11,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This summer's weather was good, so the watermelons are sweet.</font>

231
00:23:14,210 --> 00:23:17,400
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If it continues like this, then winter will be freezing.</font>

232
00:23:18,470 --> 00:23:19,750
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is it like that?</font>

233
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,700
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's like that.</font>

234
00:23:24,570 --> 00:23:28,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Since this area's located between mountains and the ocean's far away,</font>

235
00:23:28,990 --> 00:23:31,910
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">the temperature difference between summer and winter is huge.</font>

236
00:23:32,610 --> 00:23:36,000
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">The cold of a winter that follows an especially hot summer</font>

237
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:40,280
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">could probably freeze the mountain god himself.</font>

238
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,780
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Um, Uncle...</font>

239
00:23:52,770 --> 00:23:53,780
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">A scarf?</font>

240
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:55,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yep!</font>

241
00:23:55,530 --> 00:23:57,040
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Please use it in the winter, okay?</font>

242
00:23:59,660 --> 00:24:00,500
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Bye!</font>

243
00:24:03,170 --> 00:24:03,900
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Okay.</font>

244
00:24:06,450 --> 00:24:07,950
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">See you next year!</font>

245
00:24:23,860 --> 00:24:24,760
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Takegawa?</font>

246
00:24:25,390 --> 00:24:27,750
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Shouldn't you be heading to your next class soon?</font>

247
00:24:28,380 --> 00:24:30,070
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, you're right!</font>

248
00:24:30,070 --> 00:24:31,660
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Everyone left already.</font>

249
00:24:31,660 --> 00:24:33,210
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'll see you later.</font>

250
00:24:33,210 --> 00:24:34,940
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Okay! Thanks.</font>

251
00:24:56,850 --> 00:24:57,860
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank you for the food.</font>

252
00:24:57,860 --> 00:24:58,430
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">What?</font>

253
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:00,180
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're done?</font>

254
00:25:00,420 --> 00:25:03,650
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ah, you probably ate before dinner, didn't you?</font>

255
00:25:03,650 --> 00:25:05,400
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If you snack, you'll gain weight.</font>

256
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I didn't eat anything!</font>

257
00:25:07,020 --> 00:25:08,890
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Jeez. I'm gonna take a bath!</font>

258
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:40,210
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Takegawa.</font>

259
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:43,350
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ta-ke-ga-wa.</font>

260
00:25:44,750 --> 00:25:46,490
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Oh, good morning.</font>

261
00:25:46,790 --> 00:25:47,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Good morning.</font>

262
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:50,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">There, near your feet. It's frozen.</font>

263
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,430
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You'll slip. It's dangerous.</font>

264
00:26:02,120 --> 00:26:03,030
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Thank you.</font>

265
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:12,120
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's cold today.</font>

266
00:26:13,950 --> 00:26:17,810
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Haven't you been a little out of it lately?</font>

267
00:26:18,270 --> 00:26:21,330
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Actually, you've always been that way, but...</font>

268
00:26:23,050 --> 00:26:24,030
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I want to</i></font>

269
00:26:26,190 --> 00:26:27,390
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>see Gin.</i></font>

270
00:26:52,930 --> 00:26:53,830
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I want to</i></font>

271
00:26:57,170 --> 00:26:58,330
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>touch Gin.</i></font>

272
00:27:26,890 --> 00:27:28,580
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is that your new uniform?</font>

273
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:29,750
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

274
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:41,010
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Time really flies, doesn't it?</font>

275
00:27:41,620 --> 00:27:43,490
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You're already in high school, huh.</font>

276
00:27:43,490 --> 00:27:44,470
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yup.</font>

277
00:27:54,180 --> 00:27:56,610
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You don't come running at me anymore these days.</font>

278
00:27:56,610 --> 00:28:00,880
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I learned my lesson after all those beatings.</font>

279
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:09,930
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm looking forward to it.</font>

280
00:28:10,860 --> 00:28:15,640
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">In three years, when I graduate, I plan on looking for a job here.</font>

281
00:28:16,540 --> 00:28:19,710
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Then I can be with you more.</font>

282
00:28:21,220 --> 00:28:22,050
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">In autumn,</font>

283
00:28:23,110 --> 00:28:23,960
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">winter,</font>

284
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,080
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">spring...</font>

285
00:28:27,170 --> 00:28:28,160
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Always.</font>

286
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:29,660
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Right?</font>

287
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru.</font>

288
00:28:38,040 --> 00:28:40,890
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Let me tell you about myself.</font>

289
00:28:42,840 --> 00:28:44,430
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm not a spirit.</font>

290
00:28:45,450 --> 00:28:46,250
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But,</font>

291
00:28:47,510 --> 00:28:48,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm no longer human.</font>

292
00:28:50,220 --> 00:28:52,170
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It seems like I was once a human,</font>

293
00:28:52,170 --> 00:28:53,790
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">but when I was a baby,</font>

294
00:28:53,790 --> 00:28:55,730
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I was abandoned in this forest.</font>

295
00:28:56,900 --> 00:29:01,800
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'd only just been abandoned, so I cried helplessly{uh, what?}</font>

296
00:29:03,050 --> 00:29:06,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">as if to call back the parents who left me.</font>

297
00:29:08,870 --> 00:29:10,680
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">They say I didn't stop crying for a long time.</font>

298
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:21,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I should've died then,</font>

299
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:26,760
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">but the mountain god appeared and cast a spell that allowed me to continue living.</font>

300
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:32,310
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">So that I never move on.</font>

301
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,740
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I'm like a ghost.</font>

302
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:41,300
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru.</font>

303
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:44,140
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's okay if you forget about me.</font>

304
00:29:47,890 --> 00:29:51,120
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">A body that's maintained by magic is very weak.</font>

305
00:29:52,340 --> 00:29:54,380
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">If it touches a real human body,</font>

306
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:56,740
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">the spell will break and the body will disappear.</font>

307
00:29:56,740 --> 00:29:58,710
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's such a fragile thing.</font>

308
00:29:58,710 --> 00:29:59,680
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">How long can you—</font>

309
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:01,680
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Something that disappears when touched...</font>

310
00:30:02,380 --> 00:30:03,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's just like snow, isn't it?</font>

311
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:06,730
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin,</font>

312
00:30:07,860 --> 00:30:11,190
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I thought of you during winter.</font>

313
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,090
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Even during autumn</font>

314
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:15,190
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">and spring.</font>

315
00:30:16,610 --> 00:30:17,350
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin,</font>

316
00:30:18,210 --> 00:30:20,500
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">don't forget about me.</font>

317
00:30:21,970 --> 00:30:23,160
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Don't forget.</font>

318
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:30,070
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Time might separate us some day.</font>

319
00:30:31,030 --> 00:30:31,510
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But,</font>

320
00:30:32,570 --> 00:30:33,510
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">even still,</font>

321
00:30:34,150 --> 00:30:35,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">until then,</font>

322
00:30:36,390 --> 00:30:37,820
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">let's stay together.</font>

323
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Spirit festival?</font>

324
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:47,850
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">No, a summer festival held by the spirits.</font>

325
00:30:48,080 --> 00:30:49,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">There's not much of a difference.</font>

326
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:51,530
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">The nuance is completely different!</font>

327
00:30:52,060 --> 00:30:53,220
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Nuance?</font>

328
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:58,040
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">When you were little, I thought you might get scared, so I didn't invite you.</font>

329
00:30:58,790 --> 00:31:02,030
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But tonight, can you sneak out of your house?</font>

330
00:31:02,580 --> 00:31:04,850
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I've wanted to go with you for a long time.</font>

331
00:31:06,970 --> 00:31:08,920
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I-I want to go!</font>

332
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:11,710
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Meet me at eight at our usual place.</font>

333
00:31:12,210 --> 00:31:16,850
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">But a festival filled with spirits sounds a little unnerving...</font>

334
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:18,900
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">On top of that, it's at night.</font>

335
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:20,740
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Don't worry.</font>

336
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:23,330
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">On the outside, it's not very different from a human festival.</font>

337
00:31:23,930 --> 00:31:26,570
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's supposed to mimic human festivals, after all.</font>

338
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:29,760
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">And I'll protect you, Hotaru.</font>

339
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:35,030
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">When you say things that, it makes me want to glomp you.</font>

340
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:35,990
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Do it.</font>

341
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,300
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Seriously.</font>

342
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:57,350
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Wait! Wait!</font>

343
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:21,370
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's true. It's just like a human festival.</font>

344
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:23,760
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Are they all disguised as humans?</font>

345
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:25,900
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That's right. Impressive, isn't it?</font>

346
00:32:25,900 --> 00:32:29,520
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I've heard that sometimes even humans unknowingly mix in.</font>

347
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:32,890
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Like Iwa and her friends, huh?</font>

348
00:32:32,890 --> 00:32:33,700
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Who?</font>

349
00:32:37,840 --> 00:32:38,680
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru.</font>

350
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:42,050
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Tie this around your wrist.</font>

351
00:32:42,520 --> 00:32:43,470
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">You'll get lost.</font>

352
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:50,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It's just like going on a date!</font>

353
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:53,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This <i>is</i> a date.</font>

354
00:32:55,850 --> 00:32:56,750
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Shall we go?</font>

355
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:57,860
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

356
00:33:25,350 --> 00:33:26,230
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Here you go.</font>

357
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Weird.</font>

358
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:01,810
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Ew, a couple!</font>

359
00:34:01,810 --> 00:34:03,210
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hey!</font>

360
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:17,430
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Look! That kid has a tail!</font>

361
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:36,420
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I-I'm sorry!</font>

362
00:34:53,940 --> 00:34:56,860
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Wow, that was so weird!</font>

363
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:59,170
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Everyone went all out with their disguises, didn't they?</font>

364
00:34:59,170 --> 00:35:01,250
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It was like a mimicking competition!</font>

365
00:35:01,250 --> 00:35:02,670
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is it like this every year?</font>

366
00:35:02,990 --> 00:35:07,340
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah, every time summer comes around...</font>

367
00:35:09,600 --> 00:35:10,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru,</font>

368
00:35:11,160 --> 00:35:14,590
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I can no longer wait for summer to come around.</font>

369
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:21,590
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">When I'm away from you, even though I can't be around crowds, I want to go see you.</font>

370
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:47,700
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That mask...</font>

371
00:35:48,610 --> 00:35:49,400
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Have it.</font>

372
00:35:56,110 --> 00:36:02,640
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>He probably won't come to that place next summer.</i></font>

373
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:08,390
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is definitely our last...</i></font>

374
00:36:08,680 --> 00:36:10,070
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Wait!</font>

375
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:11,890
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Watch out!</font>

376
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:15,650
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Are you okay?</font>

377
00:36:15,830 --> 00:36:17,620
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah. Thank you!</font>

378
00:36:18,290 --> 00:36:19,750
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Be careful, okay?</font>

379
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:30,290
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin?</font>

380
00:36:33,330 --> 00:36:34,750
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Was that boy a human?</font>

381
00:36:41,410 --> 00:36:42,220
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin!</font>

382
00:36:43,120 --> 00:36:44,660
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Come here, Hotaru!</font>

383
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:47,110
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I can finally touch you.</font>

384
00:37:28,040 --> 00:37:29,020
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I love you.</font>

385
00:37:29,770 --> 00:37:30,470
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah.</font>

386
00:37:31,640 --> 00:37:32,950
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I love you, too.</font>

387
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,610
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Deep green.</i></font>

388
00:37:57,900 --> 00:37:59,680
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is the mountain god's forest.</i></font>

389
00:38:04,140 --> 00:38:06,830
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Hotaru. Thank you.</font>

390
00:38:07,210 --> 00:38:11,070
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">We wanted to be with Gin forever, but...</font>

391
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:16,310
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin wanted to touch a human.</font>

392
00:38:16,730 --> 00:38:20,720
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">He finally got to be hugged by a human.</font>

393
00:38:21,570 --> 00:38:23,890
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I probably won't be able to</i></font>

394
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:28,820
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>look forward to summer for a long time.</i></font>

395
00:38:29,680 --> 00:38:30,980
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>My chest will hurt.</i></font>

396
00:38:31,740 --> 00:38:33,230
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>My tears will be overflowing.</i></font>

397
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:42,980
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>But this warmth in my hands and these summer memories will live on in my heart.</i></font>

398
00:38:50,650 --> 00:38:52,440
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>So, let's go.</i></font>

399
00:38:57,330 --> 00:38:58,500
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Let us go.</i></font>

400
00:39:31,150 --> 00:39:31,160
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">{ED}</font>

401
00:39:37,600 --> 00:44:26,920
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">{\an7}<font color="#000000">m 1920 960 l 1920 1080 l 0 1080 l 0 960 l 1920 960 {p0}</font></font>

402
00:39:57,450 --> 00:40:03,380
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}<font face="Goodfish">The cicadas laugh out in song</font></font>

403
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:10,020
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}to the red evening sunset</font>

404
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:17,260
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The way back home is long</font>

405
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:24,410
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}but I promised to come here again tomorrow</font>

406
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:40,440
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The summer is in full bloom</font>

407
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:54,580
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}making you look more beautiful than ever</font>

408
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:15,750
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}I thought the tale would never end</font>

409
00:41:16,770 --> 00:41:22,550
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}but I realize now that something comes after</font>

410
00:41:23,270 --> 00:41:30,100
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The crows too took flight</font>

411
00:41:31,040 --> 00:41:38,050
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}and went somewhere far, far away</font>

412
00:41:41,730 --> 00:41:54,270
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The summer flies by</font>

413
00:41:55,840 --> 00:42:08,740
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}to hide away its treasures till next year</font>

414
00:42:56,650 --> 00:43:03,090
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}I'll never ever forget</font>

415
00:43:04,370 --> 00:43:10,570
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}those golden summer days</font>

416
00:43:11,240 --> 00:43:18,120
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}That summer which brought joy</font>

417
00:43:19,410 --> 00:43:25,700
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}to my boring everyday life</font>

418
00:43:31,390 --> 00:43:44,490
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}And look! Summer is here again</font>

419
00:43:45,310 --> 00:43:57,600
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}to help me keep my promise of that day</font>

420
00:43:58,820 --> 00:44:11,580
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The summer is still in bloom</font>

421
00:44:12,590 --> 00:44:25,410
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}making you look more beautiful than ever</font>

